platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: We love watching live streams of League of Legends, Roblox and everything in between. And there’s more to Twitch than games. The Travel and Outdoors category (you’ll find it in the Browse tab) has live animal cams. There’s even an entire channel dedicated to painter and teacher (and master of happy little trees) Bob Ross.
除了心水的遊戲直播，這個 App 中還有更多值得觀看的內容：試看看動物直播鏡頭，或者專門為「Happy Little Trees」畫家 Bob Ross 而設的整個頻道。

While we love watching live streams of our favourite games, there’s more than meets the eye. Try the many live animal cams – and even a whole channel dedicated to “happy little trees” painter Bob Ross.
このアプリは、お気に入りのゲーム実況を観られるだけではありません。様々な動物のライブカメラの中継のほか、「happy little trees」のフレーズで知られる画家、Bob Rossさんの専門チャンネルも視聴できます。
While we love watching live streams of our favourite games, there’s more than meets the eye. Try the many live animal cams–and even a whole channel dedicated to “happy little trees” painter Bob Ross.
雖然我們也喜歡在這個平台上觀看遊戲直播，但它提供的內容遠不止於此。你也能在其中找到各種動物攝影機的直播，甚至是專門播放知名風景畫家 Bob Ross 節目的頻道。
On adore regarder les retransmissions en direct de nos jeux préférés, mais ce n’est pas tout. Découvrez des images d’animaux en direct, et même une chaîne entière consacrée au peintre Bob Ross.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Broadcast, watch, chat and have fun.
